data.description: Here is your forever home! This adorable, brick house has recently been updated! With 1829 square feet under roof, this home features 3 spacious bedrooms, formal dining, large living area with a fireplace, and a bonus room that can be used for a bedroom or office! Property is just over 1/2 an acre! Back yard has wooden privacy fence and the covered back porch is a great spot to relax and unwind! This property is a must see!
